<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>비밀번호 찾기 - SchoolHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/post-new.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("../partials/header", { school: null }) %>

  <main class="container">
    <a href="/login" class="back-link">← 로그인으로 돌아가기</a>

    <section class="form-hero">
      <span class="form-label">PASSWORD</span>
      <h1>비밀번호 찾기</h1>
      <p>가입한 이메일을 입력하면 비밀번호 재설정 링크를 보내드립니다.</p>
    </section>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="error-box"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>

    <% if (success) { %>
      <div class="success-box"><%= success %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/forgot-password" method="POST" class="post-form">
      <label>
        이메일
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          autocomplete="email"
          required
        />
      </label>

      <button type="submit">재설정 메일 보내기</button>
    </form>
  </main>

  <%- include("../partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>